<Base title="What is XRP? The Complete Guide to XRP and the XRP Ledger | XRPL Stream" description="What is XRP? How the XRP Ledger works, what makes XRP different from Bitcoin and Ethereum, use cases, tokenomics, history, and how developers build on it.">
